channel.title: iHaxx Server Returning
channel.description:
Hello all,
Some of you may remember me a couple of years ago when i ust to run iHaxx and ust to bring in 8,000 unique visitors a day. I'm looking to start up another new server, ive been working on a few things over the past few weeks such as a fully working highscores system, and implementing it into my vbulletin board for my server users, Right now i need a java coder to start helping me out on a new server.
If your intrested please message me on msn
Root@iHaxx.Net
Thanks, Elux
